│ UnrollRuntimeLoopRemainder: SCEV expansion of trip count uses a value from an │
│ outer loop before establishing its LCSSA PHI in a dominating block, leading   │
│ to a dominance violation after CFG modifications create the PHI later. Adding │
│ a pre-expansion LCSSA formation call (formLCSSARecursively) at lines 760–770  │
│ ensures all required outer-loop values are in LCSSA prior to expansion,       │
│ maintaining dominance and fixing the verifier failure without altering        │
│ profitability heuristics or other logic."})                                   │
